claim.claim-text:
1. A display device comprising: 
a pixel portion in which light emitting elements are arranged in matrix; 
a monitor portion in which monitor light emitting elements are provided outside the pixel portion; 
a monitor line for detecting a potential of the monitor light emitting elements; and 
a switch for blocking a current supply to a shorted monitor light emitting element through the monitor line when one or a plurality of the monitor light emitting elements is shorted.
